Package: python3-hap-python
Architecture: all
Depends: avahi-utils, ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: python-hap-python-doc
Description: HomeKit Accessory Protocol implementation in python 3.
 With this project, you can integrate your own smart devices and add them to
 your iOS Home app. Since Siri is integrated with the Home app, you can start
 voice-control your accessories right away.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.

